description: The Trooper (Lifetime 3-5) has the experience of 8 matches under her belt; Vendetta, (Lifetime 0-2) only two. However, Vendetta was ranked higher in season two's rankings then Jade. Why was that? Why was Vendetta with 2 loses and no wins ranked higher than Jade and her one season two win? Because I saw something in Vendetta, and it was promise. I like it when I'm right.
title: The Trooper (0-0) vs. Vendetta (0-0)
